{"tid":1667223,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼害怕穆斯林?","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:02:18.000Z","uid":252659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e575bbe1aaa13193e31f5ed9d410776b9ef94c4","tid":1667223,"uid":252659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"這個族群是最好的示範<br />\n穆斯林的群體都是團結的 <br />\n一方有難八方支援<br />\n流落香港 比原居民更有實力"},{"pid":"d67b4ce30866ee75209c27df41e3a2ce51a46b8e","tid":1667223,"uid":30246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0e575bbe1aaa13193e31f5ed9d410776b9ef94c4","tid":1667223,"uid":252659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"這個族群是最好的示範<br />\n穆斯林的群體都是團結的 <br />\n一方有難八方支援<br />\n流落香港 比原居民更有實力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"因為佢地勢力唔局限係香港<br />\n而香港人勢力只局限係香港<br />\n所以佢唔會驚你"},{"pid":"7884852d8a33832c9900229ecb0a8867c3078606","tid":1667223,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64b724377050eecf841a479e3b5cda1764a2b8b7","tid":1667223,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"因為穆斯林冇奶共領袖<br />\n印尼記者單野都激嬲印尼人，但有領事館壓左落黎<br />\n今次穆斯林冇領袖幫手拆，咪要自己搞，我地睇落港共好似認晒錯咁lor"},{"pid":"b91befcadb47601376647c985efcc153be169cce","tid":1667223,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}